.el .ds Aq '
.TH grex-doctor 1  "grex-doctor " 
.SH NAME
grex\-doctor \- Run integrity checks
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBgrex\-doctor\fR [\fB\-\-fix\fR] [\fB\-\-lint\-config\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Run integrity checks
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-fix\fR
Heal gitignore drift by re\-emitting the managed block. Safety: NEVER touches the manifest or the filesystem on other checks
.TP
\fB\-\-lint\-config\fR
Run the opt\-in config\-lint check (`openspec/config.yaml` + `.omne/cfg/*.md`). Skipped by default
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
